Thank you for using our app — Study Planner & Time Organizer.
Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your information while providing a helpful and enjoyable experience.

🧩 Data Collection

This app does not collect any personal data such as names, emails, or photos.

Routine technical information (e.g., IP address, device type, operating system version, and timestamps) may be collected automatically for analytics, maintenance, and security monitoring.

This technical data cannot personally identify specific users and is used only to improve performance.

🧱 Local Storage

All your notes, flashcards, mind maps, and weekly schedules are stored locally on your device.

We do not upload or transfer your personal study data to any servers.

💰 Advertisements

The app uses Google AdMob to display ads.

AdMob may use cookies or device identifiers to provide personalized ads and measure ad performance.

You can learn more about Google’s data practices here:
🔗 https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads

🍪 Cookies and Similar Technologies

Cookies or similar technologies may be used to save your app preferences and enhance the user experience.

You can manage or disable cookies through your device or browser settings at any time.

🔔 Notifications

The app may send reminders and notifications to help you stay organized.

You can disable notifications from your device settings if you prefer.

🔐 Data Security

Data transmitted through the internet (such as ads) is encrypted in transit.

While we strive to use secure means to protect your information, please note that no method of data transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

🤝 Data Sharing

We do not share user data with third parties, except as necessary for the operation of integrated services (e.g., AdMob).

These services have their own privacy policies governing their use of data.

🧹 Data Deletion

If any non-personal data is collected through third-party services, you may request its deletion at any time by contacting us via the email below.

We will delete any data as soon as reasonably possible upon receiving your request.

🔗 Links to Third-Party Sites

The app may contain links to external websites.

We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those third-party sites.

